reviewText: I thought I was ordering the dvd of Silence of the Lambs.  I received a dvd of several unwanted films but Silence of the Lambs was among them.  I had/have no interest in the other films and don't have the exclusive cover art I expected of The Silence of the Lambs.  Rather disappointing.

Awesome DVD.  I have watched this movie many, many times.  She shows her braveness going to talk with Dr. Lector.  She is just a rookie in the FBI (actually still in training)  and takes on an adventure that proves she will be a good FBI Agent.  It keeps you on the edge of your seat.  It is an excellent movie.  zsarsorrenson@gmail.com
